    <item>
      <title>西班牙保守党赢得地方选举，社会主义者退却</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/spain-conservatives-win-regional-election-as-socialists-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙最强大的反对党轻松赢得了加利西亚地区选举，而总理佩德罗·桑切斯的社会党在他寻求特赦加泰罗尼亚分离主义者以来的第一次选举测试中失去了约三分之一的席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/spain-conservatives-win-regional-election-as-socialists-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 22:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥抗议者在总统选举前的“民主游行”中猛烈抨击奥夫拉多尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/mexican-protesters-blast-amlo-in-march-for-democracy-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥抗议者周日走上街头进行“民主游行”，称总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔可能不公平地影响拉丁美洲第二大经济体即将举行的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/mexican-protesters-blast-amlo-in-march-for-democracy-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 22:00:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国停火投票临近，斯塔默敦促结束加沙战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/starmer-urges-end-to-gaza-fighting-as-uk-vote-on-ceasefire-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国反对派领袖凯尔·斯塔默表示，加沙“战斗现在必须停止”，他正在准备本周另一场敏感的议会投票，这可能会重新引发工党内部的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/starmer-urges-end-to-gaza-fighting-as-uk-vote-on-ceasefire-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 21:59:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼基·黑利抨击特朗普对“英雄”纳瓦尔尼之死保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/nikki-haley-assails-trump-for-silence-on-hero-navalny-s-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前南卡罗来纳州州长尼基·黑利攻击唐纳德·特朗普的外交政策，谴责前总统对俄罗斯反对派领导人亚历山大·纳瓦尔尼之死保持沉默。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/nikki-haley-assails-trump-for-silence-on-hero-navalny-s-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 21:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
