    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友正在谋划美国撤退的世界</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/ukraine-s-allies-are-gaming-out-a-world-in-which-the-us-retreats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约成员国现在私下谈论俄罗斯对其中一个国家的袭击，认为这是一种需要紧急应对的危险，因为他们越来越怀疑美国是否会维持其作为北约一部分保护欧洲的传统角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/ukraine-s-allies-are-gaming-out-a-world-in-which-the-us-retreats</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥城数千人游行反对执政党总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-18/thousands-rail-against-mexico-s-president-and-ruling-party-in-march-for-democracy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥城（美联社）——周日，数千名身着粉红色斗篷的示威者在墨西哥和国外的城市中游行，他们称之为“民主游行”，目标是在该国 6 月 2 日选举之前针对该国执政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-18/thousands-rail-against-mexico-s-president-and-ruling-party-in-march-for-democracy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列将发动拉法攻势除非人质在斋月回家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/israel-to-launch-rafah-offensive-unless-hostages-home-by-ramadan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列无公务部长本尼·甘茨周日表示，除非在三月斋月假期之前释放仍被哈马斯扣押的人质，否则以色列将在加沙拉法地区发动地面攻势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/israel-to-launch-rafah-offensive-unless-hostages-home-by-ramadan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 17:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
